<title>
    <%= title %>
</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.4.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" />
<script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/00d76a4bef.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css'>
<script src="/js/jquery.js"></script>


<%- include('header'); -%>
    <section class="featured">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <h1 id="myHeader" class="text-4xl">
                <%= title %>
            </h1>
        </div>
    </section>
    <div class="max-w-fit md:py-[20] py-3 flex mx-4 sm:flex-row flex-col justify-around">
        <div class="basis-[50%] pb-5 mx-auto overflow-hidden">
            <p class="py-3 text-justify  text-3xl font-serif hover:text-blue-700">
                Adding employee names to an attendance management system improves its accuracy and efficiency.
                Personalized records help in generating precise reports and understanding attendance patterns better.
                Overall, having employee names in the system helps management to handle attendance more effectively,
                ensuring smooth operations and accurate record-keeping.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class=" basis-[50%] h-2/3 flex flex-col items-center justify-center m-auto">
            <form action="/addemp/" method="POST"
                class="bg-slate-400 flex flex-col items-center justify-center w-full sm:w-[90%] mx-4 rounded-lg">
                <p class="text-green-700 text-2xl font-serif">
                    Add new employee
                </p>
                <input aria-label="Enter employee name" type="text" name="empname" placeholder="Employee name" required
                    autocomplete="off"
                    class="text-sm text-gray-base w-3/4 mt-3 mr-3 py-3 px-4  border  border-gray-200 rounded mb-2" />
                <input aria-label="Enter joining year" type="number" min="2006" name="joinyr" placeholder="Joining year"
                    class="text-sm text-gray-base w-3/4 mr-3  py-3 px-4  border border-gray-200  rounded mb-2" />
                <select name="cmbGender" id="cmbGender" required
                    class="text-sm w-3/4 mr-3  py-3 px-4 border border-gray-200  rounded mb-2">
                    <option value="Male" selected>Male</option>
                    <option value="Female">Female</option>
                </select>
                <input aria-label="Enter mobile" type="number" name="txtmob" placeholder="Mobile number" required
                    min="5555555555" max="9999999999" autocomplete="off"
                    class="text-sm text-gray-base w-3/4 mr-3  py-3 px-4  border border-gray-200  rounded mb-2" />
                <input aria-label="Enter remarks" type="text" name="rmrk" placeholder="Remarks (if any)"
                    autocomplete="off"
                    class="text-sm text-gray-base w-3/4 mr-3  py-3 px-4  border border-gray-200  rounded mb-2" />

                <button type="submit" class="bg-green-400 py-3 w-3/4 mb-4 mr-3 hover:bg-green-600 hover:rounded-full text-sm">
                    Submit
                </button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
    <%- include('footer'); -%>